comments.en:
The title theme. A strange song like never before.
I really don't think there needs to be a song for a motionless title screen, but since it'd feel lonely without it I always have a song for the title.
But I feel as if it feels lonelier with the song. (^^;

VIVIT's theme.

When thinking of a maid, people get the image of a girl with glasses who's weak to sunlight, but this time, I made this song with my image of a maid.

Well, it always happens, but... I'm pretty sure this isn't an Asian style of song.(^^;

